lastCommitMessage: refactor: adapt file upload service to new SDK and improve file validation
- Updated the file upload service to utilize the new FileUploadResult and FileUploadApi from the agora_market_dart_sdk.
- Changed references from tempUrl to presignedUrl for consistency in file upload results.
- Enhanced file validation logic to include checks for archive file types and improved error handling for unsupported file types.
- Cleaned up unused code and improved logging for better debugging and tracking of file upload processes.
These changes aim to streamline file upload functionality and enhance overall code clarity.
